Blah! I meant the CF with Grimmler instead of the Ark. You want to change it, 
Kinger, or should we just go along with the Ark?

::Prowl::

"Love!" Prowl yells as Iron Raptor leans against the wall, taking a few steps 
to close the distance between them.

"Are you allright?" he asks, looking extremely concerned as he puts a hand on 
her shoulder.
